DESCRIPTION:Join a weekly walk every Tuesday morning to enjoy the 1.4-mile
  round-trip loop at the Petaluma River Park. You’ll be accompanied by ot
 hers looking to soak in the beauty of the park in a group setting. PLEASE 
 NOTE: In the event of rain\, River Park Walks will be canceled. Thank you 
 for your understanding. .fe-block-dc7661ff82513b396fe4 {mix-blend-mode: \;
  }
LOCATION:Petaluma River Park \, 100 East D Street\, Petaluma\, CA\, 94952
